Cobblers Wardrobe is both a designer consignment store and shoe repair service. Our aim is to help you find a new home for your once loved possessions. We welcome and sell all kinds of new or gently used apparel, accessories and unique pieces on your behalf. We are always looking for vintage and one of a kind luxury items.

At Cobblers Wardrobe we offer the finest traditional and high fashion shoe repair service, as well as selling a comprehensive range of shoe and leather care products in store.

For more information about this service visit: www.isaacjackman.ie For all other queries please call us or make an appointment: info@cobblerswardrobe.com
